	* engine/cvm_call.c (_ILPackCVMStackArgs): Remove unused variable x.

	* engine/cvmc_except.c (CVMCoder_OutputExceptionTable): Remove unused
	variable parent.

	* engine/lib_delegate.c (_ILCoderGenDelegateCtor): Remove unused variable
	classInfo.
