	an #ifdef IL_USE_CVM.

	* engine/cvm_except.c: Move the functions in the global definitions to
	system.c.

	* engine/cvm_ptr.c: Move the function _ILSystemObjectSetField to system.c.

	* engine/cvmc.c: Wrap the contents in an #ifdef IL_USE_CVM.

