	* engine/jitc.c: Add signature for _ILJitGetExceptionStackTrace. Pass
	structs by ref in _ILJitCompileInternal. Include the new files jitc_diag.c
	and jitc_labels.c. Move _ILJitGetCallingMethod to jitc_diag.c.

